<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l5">VVir die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc . daʒ für vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Rumel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l7">der <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_line_1577277735125_1261"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab></add> vnd hat vns <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> . vvie daʒ <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Poſſeck <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l8">cʒum <expan>Rotemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> dem . <expan cert="unknown">C .</expan> Swarcʒen vom lewbleinſhof <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l9"><expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> ix kẅe vnd ij pferd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> het / dıe Er Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l10"><expan>vvidergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab . Als vns der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> geſagt vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l11">gebeten hat / das vvir darümb 
<del rend="strikethrough">deſſelb </del> des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>Poſſecke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l12">freund <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd alſo <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l14">poſſecken . 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd aller </del> <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> helffer vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l13">dyner </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> aller der die <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l15">
<del rend="strikethrough">verdacht ſein </del> gut freund v̈mb dıe tat ongeuerde / Mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l16"><expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> franciſci </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="163v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
